data.description: ***Seller Offering $12K Towards Buyers Closing Costs &/or Rate Buy Down.***Located In New 2024 Prairieville High School District.***Meticulously Maintained Inside & Beautifully Landscaped Outside, You'll Love This Centrally Located Oasis in Hidden Cove Subdivision. 4 Beds, 3 Baths, Triple Split Open Floor Plan w/11 Ft Ceilings, 8 Ft Int Doors, Brick Fireplace, Granite Kit, Bath & Laundry Counters. Window Blinds Throughout. Great Trim Package w/Wood Trimmed Windows, Antique Wood Beams, Extensive Crown Moldings, Ship-Lap Walls & Cabinets Galore! Chefs Kitchen w/Walk-In Pantry, SS Farm Sink, Professional Series SS Appliances including Gas Range, Dishwasher & Island Microwave.  Impressive EnSuite Master Bed/Bath & Massive Walk-In Closet. Stained Wood Ceilings on Front & Rear Porch! Ascension Top-rated Schools Too! Move in Ready, Stands Out at This Price Point, & Should Be Your Next Home.
